title: Openstreetmap, Finland Points of Interest, Finland, 2008

description: This data set shows various points of interest throughout the country of Finland. Points of interest include, but are not limited to the following: Hospitals, schools, post offices, restaurants, fuel, parking, places of worship, churches, monuments, pubs, nightclubs, campsites, and monuments. data was uploaded as a poly point shape file.
